title: Cartel Cash For Democrats? With Cassy Garcia and Tudor Dixon
itunes:title: Cartel Cash For Democrats? With Cassy Garcia and Tudor Dixon
description:
The Hispanics of South Texas were solid Democratic voters for decades. Now, they're flooding over to the GOP in droves. One reason is that the Democrats have totally capitulated to the drug cartels swarming over the border. Latina GOP House candidate Cassy Garcia joins to tell how her opponent Henry Cuellar received money linked to the murderous Zetas cartel. Plus, Tudor Dixon joins to discuss her final push to topple Gretchen Whitmer in Michigan.
